is a Japanese manga series written by Kappy and illustrated by Masaaki Tsuzuki. It began serialization on Shueisha's Shōnen Jump+ manga service in April 2025.
Publication
Written by Kappy and illustrated by Masaaki Tsuzuki, War of the Adults began serialization on Shueisha's Shōnen Jump+ manga service on April 5, 2025. Its chapters have been compiled into two  volumes as of September 2025.
The series' chapters are simultaneously published in English on Shueisha's Manga Plus app.
